b7 ff5 fs21 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thoughts, we should turn them over to God for crucifixion and ask, believe, </div><div class="t m251 x9 h37 ybb8 ff5 fs21 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and claim His power. </div><div class="t m471 x6f h35 y1a1 ff1 fs21 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">PERSONAL APPLICATIONS: </div><div class="t m59f x42 h37 y1a3 ff5 fs21 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Can you think of any fruits of the Spirit to add to Paul&apos;s list? Read the </div><div class="t m5a0 x6f h37 y1a4 ff5 fs21 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fruits of the Spirit as listed by Paul in Galatians 4:22. Select those fruits </div><div class="t m492 x6f h37 y1a5 ff5 fs21 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">which would affect the following areas and relationships: </div><div class="t m5a1 x42 h37 ybb9 ff5 fs21 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m153 x1d h37 y1a7 ff5 fs21 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Marriage </div><div class="t m105 x2a h37 y1a7 ff5 fs21 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m23e x3c h37 ybb9 ff5 fs21 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. Health </div><div class="t m275 x14 h37 y1a7 ff5 fs21 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. Personal </div><div class="t m42b xdc h37 y1a8 ff5 fs21 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fulfillment </div><div class="t m42b xec h1c ybba ff7 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"><span class="fc0 sc0"> </span><span class="_ _c"> </span><span class="fc0 sc0"> </span><span class="_ _d"> </span><span class="fc0 sc0"> </span><span class="_ _e"> </span><span class="fc0 sc0"> </span><span class="_ _f"> </span><span class="fc0 sc0"> </span></div><div class="t m5a2 x42 h37 y1ac ff5 fs21 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t mdd x1d h37 y1ac ff5 fs21 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Children </div><div class="t m39d x3c h37 y98c ff5 fs21 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. Outreach </div><div class="t m105 xc8 h37 y98c ff5 fs21 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t maa x48 h37 y98c ff5 fs21 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">8. Neighbors and </div><div class="t m9b x68 h37 y98d ff5 fs21 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">friends </div><div class="t m9b x58 h1c ybbb ff7 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"><span class="fc0 sc0"> </span><span class="_ _10"> </span><span class="f